"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/897254","Cabinet Office","false","2018-05-15","<p>The information requested falls within the responsibility of the UK Statistics Authority. I have asked the Authority to reply.</p><p> </p>","Norwich North","Chloe Smith",,"2018-05-15T16:25:55.737Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/897254/answer","Biography information for Chloe Smith","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/897254/answer","PQ141038 and PQ141039 draft  (1).docx","PQ141038 and PQ141039 draft  (1).docx","UKSA Response ","UKSA Response ","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/897254/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2018-05-03","Unemployment: Dyslexia","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what estimate he has made of the number of people with dyslexia who are (a) unemployed and (b) not in training or further education.","false","Biography information for Mrs Emma Lewell-Buck","South Shields","Mrs Emma Lewell-Buck","141038"
